{"product_id":"regular-ringer-cropped-tee-ii","title":"REGULAR RINGER CROPPED TEE II","description":"\u003cp\u003e240 GSM. Premium Fabric. Minimal Design. 100% Combed Cotton. Ringer Style Neck \u0026amp; Sleeves. Gender-Neutral. Regular-Fit Cropped Silhouette. Combed \u0026amp; Bio-washed.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003cp\u003eThis premium 240 GSM ringer cropped T-shirt from Drip Studios blends classic aesthetics with a modern cropped silhouette. Designed with contrasting ringer detailing on the neckline and sleeve hems, it delivers a subtle vintage-inspired edge while maintaining a clean, minimal look. The regular cropped fit offers balanced structure with everyday comfort, making it easy to style across casual and streetwear outfits. Crafted from 100% combed cotton and finished with a bio-wash, the fabric feels soft, breathable, and durable for long-lasting wear. With no prints or graphics, this tee remains a versatile wardrobe essential built for effortless styling.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCare Guide\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003eMachine wash the T-shirt inside out with similar colors using cold water. Avoid bleach. Tumble dry on low heat or air dry to maintain fabric quality and structure. Store in a cool, dry place to preserve the finish.\u003c\/p\u003e\n\n\u003ch4\u003eCore Features\u003c\/h4\u003e\n\u003cp\u003e240 GSM premium cotton fabric for a balanced, structured feel. Regular-fit cropped silhouette designed for modern everyday wear. Classic ringer neckline and sleeve contrast detailing. Minimal blank design for versatile styling. Gender-neutral construction suitable for multiple body types. Combed and bio-washed cotton for enhanced softness, breathability, and durability.\u003c\/p\u003e","brand":"DRIPDRIP","offers":[{"title":"S","offer_id":47546240663706,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"M","offer_id":47546240696474,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":true},{"title":"L","offer_id":47546240729242,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false},{"title":"XL","offer_id":47546240762010,"sku":"blind-drip","price":1399.0,"currency_code":"INR","in_stock":false}],"thumbnail_url":"\/\/cdn.shopify.com\/s\/files\/1\/0717\/2584\/2586\/files\/DSC00363copy_11zon.jpg?v=1772787384","url":"https:\/\/dripdrip.in\/products\/regular-ringer-cropped-tee-ii","provider":"DRIP STUDIOS","version":"1.0","type":"link"}